{
  "stem": "9943.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The, the grandfather-- him, my mother's father, I got to know later when we returned back to-- from Rostov, back home.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That happened in 1922, close to 1923.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now the life in Rostov, which was from 1916 till '22, was already a turbulent life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Initially, my father opened what was called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were sending out packages, just packing up and sending away things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a kind of a bureau of, of transporting things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know what you would--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Rostov to wherever in Russia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, something like this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was-- that-- what, what he was making a living there, in Rostov.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it was an interesting life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We're in this quarter that-- what I was starting to say-- that where we lived on this Romanov [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was on the corner of [NON-ENGLISH], it was called.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So there was a, a factory of cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were making boxes-- in beautiful boxes with-- they're packing cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were playing with all those.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were getting those boxes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so I started to go to movies, start a kind of big-city life, going to theater, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] ballet.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was a big city, Rostov-- relatively.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "For me, it was a very big city, a beautiful city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We used to go to the gardens there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I don't know in what to-- what actually-- to what kind of details to go in about it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But you, you developed like a, a city child.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And life was OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Until-- then came 1917, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In the gymnasium, they changed the, the prayer from, from-- praying for the-- for the health of the czar changed to Christ loving army.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
